HEADWORD: Beamed
<hw>Beamed</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Furnished with beams,
as the head of a stag.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Tost his <qex>beamed</qex> frontlet to the sky.</q> <rj><qau>Sir
